title: Guard Dog Collegiate Hybrid Case for iPhone 6 Plus / 6s Plus – Alabama Crimson Tide – Clear with Black
features: Hybrid Cases for iPhone 6 Plus / 6s Plus from Guard Dog offer dual-layer protection. The inner layer is a soft, colorful silicone that wraps around your phone acting as a bumper. The silicone layer comes over the top of your iPhone 6 Plus / 6s Plus, helping to prevent scratches to your screen. The outer shell holds the silicone in place and helps protect your phone from dings and scratches.

These Clear cases add an element of fun to your style - the outer plastic shell is clear matte, allowing the silicone color to shine through. This unique design gives a frosted look to your iPhone 6 Plus / 6s Plus case while giving you the same Guard Dog protection you expect.
Officially Licensed Hybrid Cases sport the Alabama Crimson Tide logo in full color print.
Hybrid Cases are sleek and lightweight - quality protection without unnecessary bulk or weight!
